flowchart TB
  Start[Symptom observed] --> Scope[Confirm namespace + context]
  Scope --> Events[oc get events / describe]
  Events --> Status{Pod status?}
  Status -- Pending --> Pending[Quota/Limit/Node capacity\ncheck messages]
  Status -- CrashLoop --> Logs[oc logs --previous]
  Status -- Running but broken --> Net[Service/Route/DNS/NetworkPolicy]
  Pending --> Fix[Apply minimal fix]
  Logs --> Fix
  Net --> Fix
  Fix --> Verify[Re-test + re-check events]
  Verify --> End[Done + note the command]
